        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3668011843" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12691119519655283277">The New Atheism has some wonderful chapters, but ultimately I was left with more interest in the other works Stenger routinely cites than this book itself. I&apos;m not sure how much new content it brings forward, but it&apos;s a nice overview.</span>
  <span id="freeText12691119519655283277" style="display:none">The New Atheism has some wonderful chapters, but ultimately I was left with more interest in the other works Stenger routinely cites than this book itself. I'm not sure how much new content it brings forward, but it's a nice overview.</span>
