<li class='cover' id='bookCover_15818294'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15818294-the-myth-of-persecution"><img alt="The Myth of Persecution: How Early Christians Invented a Story of Martyrdom" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1366277434l/15818294._SX98_.jpg" />
