<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13147382-proving-history"><img alt="Proving History: Bayes&#39;s Theorem and the Quest for the Historical Jesus" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1365463922l/13147382._SX98_.jpg" />
